<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:12:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾在中国威胁下增加导弹演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-increase-missile-drills-amid-china-threats-2024-03-05/</link><description>台湾国防部长邱国正周二表示，在中国加大军事压力迫使台湾接受其主权主张之际，台湾武装部队今年将增加举行导弹演习的次数。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:40:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-increase-missile-drills-amid-china-threats-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国全国人大：你需要知道什么</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-npc-what-you-need-know-2024-03-05/</link><description>中国议会、全国人民代表大会（NPC）于周二开幕，国务院总理李强在天安门广场人民大会堂发表了他的首次工作报告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:16:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-npc-what-you-need-know-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国全国人大会议令人失望，股市下滑，比特币接近纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-05/</link><description>中国股市周二下跌，拖累亚洲股市，因为投资者对北京在为期一周的全国人民代表大会年度会议开幕之际支持经济的计划表示失望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国经济转型承诺未能给人留下深刻印象，油价延续跌势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-extends-fall-chinas-pledge-transform-economy-fails-impress-2024-03-05/</link><description>周二，全球最大原油进口国中国承诺在经济增长缓慢的情况下实现经济转型，油价连续第二天下跌，因为新冠疫情大流行未能打动担心消费放缓的投资者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-extends-fall-chinas-pledge-transform-economy-fails-impress-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示2月份中国服务业活动增长势头减弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-growth-momentum-softens-feb-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-03-05/</link><description>周二的一项私营部门调查显示，中国 2 月份服务业活动增长放缓，商业信心连续第二个月放缓，企业自 11 月份以来首次裁员。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-growth-momentum-softens-feb-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，AMD 在销售专为中国定制的人工智能芯片方面遇到了美国障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amd-hits-us-roadblock-selling-specific-ai-chips-china-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-05/</link><description>据彭博社周一报道，超微半导体公司在销售专为中国市场定制的人工智能芯片方面遇到了美国政府的障碍，这是华盛顿打击向中国出口先进技术的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/amd-hits-us-roadblock-selling-specific-ai-chips-china-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>美元是中国新闻的旁观者，日元考虑利率风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-spectator-china-news-yen-ponders-rate-risks-2024-03-05/</link><description>周二，美元兑人民币保持稳定，市场消化了中国的一系列政策声明，而东京通胀的反弹似乎让日本距离结束负利率又近了一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-spectator-china-news-yen-ponders-rate-risks-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国将完善生育政策加大对老年人的支持力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-improve-childbirth-policies-boost-support-elderly-2024-03-05/</link><description>周二，两份官方政府报告称，中国将完善支持生育的政策，其中还详细介绍了通过提高福利和基本养老金以及推动私人养老金制度来支持不断增长的老年人口的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:18:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-improve-childbirth-policies-boost-support-elderly-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国不再提及台湾“和平统一”；国防开支增加7.2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-drops-peaceful-reunification-reference-taiwan-raises-defence-spending-by-2024-03-05/</link><description>路透社周二审阅的一份官方工作报告显示，中国今年将增加国防开支7.2%，与去年持平，但高于政府经济增长预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-drops-peaceful-reunification-reference-taiwan-raises-defence-spending-by-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>聘请中国外交官、前反腐官员有望担任下一任外交部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/engaging-chinese-diplomat-former-anti-graft-official-tipped-be-next-foreign-2024-03-05/</link><description>本周，在北京的外交官们出席中国人大年度会议时，一位引人注目的中国官员是一位富有魅力的牛津大学毕业生，许多人预计他将成为下一任外交部长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/engaging-chinese-diplomat-former-anti-graft-official-tipped-be-next-foreign-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国发誓要“转型”经济，目标稳定增长5%左右</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-targets-2024-gdp-growth-around-5-government-work-report-2024-03-05/</link><description>中国总理李强周二表示，中国今年的经济增长目标是5%左右，努力转变发展方式、抑制工业产能过剩、化解房地产业风险、削减地方政府浪费性支出。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-targets-2024-gdp-growth-around-5-government-work-report-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称已对仁爱礁菲律宾船只采取措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-it-takes-measures-against-philippine-vessels-second-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国海警周二表示，对非法侵入南海有争议岛礁仁爱礁附近海域的菲律宾船只采取了管制措施。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 23:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-it-takes-measures-against-philippine-vessels-second-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：风险反弹势头增强，中国公布目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-04/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:48:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国销量跌至一年多来最低水平后，特斯拉股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-skid-after-february-china-sales-slump-2024-03-04/</link><description>特斯拉股价周一下跌超过 7%，此前该公司 2 月份在中国的销量下降，该公司在中国的销量可能会在农历新年假期期间面临放缓。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:25:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-skid-after-february-china-sales-slump-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>法国考虑处罚以遏制超快时尚品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/france-mulls-penalties-rein-ultra-fast-fashion-brands-2024-03-04/</link><description>法国占多数的议员在一项新法案中提议，对中国 Shein 等产品周转速度超快的时尚品牌应处以最高其服装售价 50% 的罚款，以抵消其对环境的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:13:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/france-mulls-penalties-rein-ultra-fast-fashion-brands-2024-03-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>